{"tid":1562923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「《願榮光歸香港》管弦樂團及合唱團版」嘅手足入一入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-12T08:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:36:19.000Z","uid":47541,"like":306,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"11ecc2d744751b544e2ed86e9797df1ece1c09ff","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"首先奉上link一條，大家睇多幾次：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=9ee89304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g</a><br />\n<br />\n首先好多謝作曲作詞演奏合唱同埋production嘅手足，真係好高汁！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有見及唔少外國人都開始睇個mv，又有唔少出名嘅人係twitter上share，<br />\n希望手足可以加番英文係title同description，比外國人更加易明個mv同歌係做咩。<br />\n如果可以既話，可以開放埋subtitle，我地可以幫手加唔同language既subtitle！</span><br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f128b4a2c1c6d81d2f595f3372af2c74819d914b","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff07091b0d75f347276c9b699aaa4ea7c09e204","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:09:48.000Z","msg":"推到比手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f04c029b58092c8c1f1b5cdde07dbb05d4f8da6","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"個mv真係好好j"},{"pid":"51cf9277ee28aea8c85fc2d6e4807f5a8d8aa173","tid":1562923,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5c7472815bdf59d99f6a9e4ab625dbdedb846014","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"For the tears that we shed on this soil<br />\nFor the anguish we had in this turmoil<br />\nWe keep our heads up, our voices strong<br />\nMay freedom root in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nFor the fear that looms overhead<br />\nFor the hope that moves us ahead<br />\nWe march in blood, our martyrs along<br />\nMay freedom glow in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDeepest night we shall not be in fright<br />\nIn the mist, a new day breaks with chants and light<br />\nStand with us, with virtuous minds and unbending spines<br />\nThe pearl we hold will always shine<br />\n<br />\nCome children of our motherland<br />\nThe time has come to wage a revolution<br />\nFreedom and liberty belong to this land<br />\nMay glory be to Hong Kong"},{"pid":"962a00df005bc21fb41fc0bc084c4f7d6e0b7428","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"呢個version好多外國人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15d5d80a7059ff3beded39597bc5792b232aab6","tid":1562923,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1a28e7ce6a1b06f3f7e8026669d27136f65ff06","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"lik