\n日期: 9月15日 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 下午3時<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n終點: 遮打道行人專用道<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef21ec0060d984259f9fcd79fc7622106aa5129","tid":1562923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"[2百萬人再集結] 915民陣大遊行<br />\n日期: 9月15日 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 下午3時<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n終點: 遮打道行人專用道<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958043b95d462e5054ceaf2d86f4175820450b11","tid":1562923,"uid":303911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"82bb0b3544fb913bf12e2cfb59de40d3917301cf","tid":1562923,"uid":113022,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5c7472815bdf59d99f6a9e4ab625dbdedb846014","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"For the tears that we shed on this soil<br />\nFor the anguish we had in this turmoil<br />\nWe keep our heads up, our voices strong<br />\nMay freedom root in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nFor the fear that looms overhead<br />\nFor the hope that moves us ahead<br />\nWe march in blood, our martyrs along<br />\nMay freedom glow in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDeepest night we shall not be in fright<br />\nIn the mist, a new day breaks with chants and light<br />\nStand with us, with virtuous minds and unbending spines<br />\nThe pearl we hold will always shine<br />\n<br />\nCome children of our motherland<br />\nThe time has come to wage a revolution<br />\nFreedom and liberty belong to this land<br />\nMay glory be to Hong Kong"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"另一位巴打既version高汁好多<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\nIn angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\nWith rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\nWe rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 <br />\nAs we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\nWith eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\nIn faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\nOur flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 <br />\nFree this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\nStars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\nStorms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 <br />\nWe shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 <br />\nThis perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 <br />\nDetermined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\nWith hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\nGlory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\nFreedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\nLiberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\nGlory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"7a9ef9523bfb64507c8d3cbabbf59aeacedcddd1","tid":1562923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"[2百萬人再集結] 915民陣大遊行<br />\n日期: 9月15日 (星期日)<br />\n時間: 下午3時<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n終點: 遮打道行人專用道<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6ff66a7659585f89d312201a140f297501dd17","tid":1562923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kingkongcrew/status/1170322218565300229?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkingkongcrew%2Fstatus%2F1170322218565300229%3Fs%3D19&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=a364034a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkingkongcrew%2Fstatus%2F1170322218565300229%3Fs%3D19&h=a1c5f47d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kingkongcrew/status/1170322218565300229?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n再推！<br />\nretweets仲係太少。「核彈文宣」高質片解釋畀外國人聽點解要杯葛花木蘭同支持香港人權及民主法案"},{"pid":"7d63eac65194b844bf0dc28e900893701b1ac191","tid":1562923,"uid":93209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hi-zlWtc21M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhi-zlWtc21M&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=421600a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hi-zlWtc21M</a><br />\n幫手report 藍絲偷國歌"},{"pid":"a086b8c131d9812776080fb1898c7dba67f21ec4","tid":1562923,"uid":237528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n［重要］外媒贊我地玩人鏈唱karaoke式抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n我系香港人呀屌￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人繼續自high 啦 繼續今天我 又比d 掌聲自己<br />\n屌你地老母 ￼<br />\n出面行動post 又唔見你地推得咁落力￼<br />\n十幾個國歌post ￼Twitter 又全部國歌<br />\n新屋嶺義士呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTwitter 文宣又唔宣掦新屋嶺義士被打強姦情況￼<br />\n義士正式成為condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新屋嶺系核彈 港版集中營<br />\n全世界集中火力 tag #sunukling # Chinazi #xinjiang #policestate #warcrime<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家人權法唔系100%通過￼<br />\n可以加辣亦可以減辣<br />\n之前就受害者模式<br />\n依家就勝利者模式唱國歌<br />\n你估依家美國會唔會幫你加辣￼￼￼<br />\n未通過之前好心大家扮下野啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續唱美國國歌 揮美國國旗<br />\n同埋做好文宣 咩都好形造到我地有幾慘得幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631aa21b3f277ee0c6297d550bd5c1ebcdabadbf","tid":1562923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"The FIVE demands of the protest<br />\n<br />\n1. Full withdrawal of the extradition bill<br />\n<br />\n2. A commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality<br />\n<br />\n3. Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n4. Amnesty for arrested protesters<br />\n<br />\n5. Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and<br />\nthe Chief Executive<br />\n<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS,<br />\nNOT ONE LESS.<br />\nLIBERATE HONG KONG,<br />\nREVOLUTION OF OUR TIMES<br />\n<br />\n撇除政府問題，淨係計警隊，再淨係計721 85 811 新屋嶺 CCTV直送 831，已經夠哂理由比示威者做任何野，包括以武制暴 以眼還眼 百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，立即實行雙普選，推翻港共政權<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，但大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動<br />\n#抵制一切鐵路沿線所有商戶"},{"pid":"d3cc2a4cd0d8a3a95c18cbfda43d5322b45814d8","tid":1562923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 幫襯良心商店<br />\n2. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n3. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚十點咆哮！（有人話改九點）<br />\n5. 健身+運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=77475ec4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會，陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.12 @Template End@"},{"pid":"0fb22ddee46cfdd43e87bcced8c8e795b73a1e85","tid":1562923,"uid":67168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2936d055c7592ca3409a827245eea84b26318355","tid":1562923,"uid":23993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"會有英文版同唱K版 等多幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》管弦樂團及合唱團SATB版 （中詞） MV<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1561084\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1561084</a>"},{"pid":"a58132bd37516e20f3d11786791bf1da7fa3b6a1","tid":1562923,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a086b8c131d9812776080fb1898c7dba67f21ec4","tid":1562923,"uid":237528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n［重要］外媒贊我地玩人鏈唱karaoke式抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n我系香港人呀屌￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人繼續自high 啦 繼續今天我 又比d 掌聲自己<br />\n屌你地老母 ￼<br />\n出面行動post 又唔見你地推得咁落力￼<br />\n十幾個國歌post ￼Twitter 又全部國歌<br />\n新屋嶺義士呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTwitter 文宣又唔宣掦新屋嶺義士被打強姦情況￼<br />\n義士正式成為condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新屋嶺系核彈 港版集中營<br />\n全世界集中火力 tag #sunukling # Chinazi #xinjiang #policestate #warcrime<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家人權法唔系100%通過￼<br />\n可以加辣亦可以減辣<br />\n之前就受害者模式<br />\n依家就勝利者模式唱國歌<br />\n你估依家美國會唔會幫你加辣￼￼￼<br />\n未通過之前好心大家扮下野啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br