ng Kong<br />\n<br />\nFor the fear that looms overhead<br />\nFor the hope that moves us ahead<br />\nWe march in blood, our martyrs along<br />\nMay freedom glow in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDeepest night we shall not be in fright<br />\nIn the mist, a new day breaks with chants and light<br />\nStand with us, with virtuous minds and unbending spines<br />\nThe pearl we hold will always shine<br />\n<br />\nCome children of our motherland<br />\nThe time has come to wage a revolution<br />\nFreedom and liberty belong to this land<br />\nMay glory be to Hong Kong"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"另一位巴打既version高汁好多<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\nIn angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\nWith rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\nWe rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 <br />\nAs we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\nWith eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\nIn faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\nOur flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 <br />\nFree this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\nStars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\nStorms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 <br />\nWe shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 <br />\nThis perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 <br />\nDetermined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\nWith hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\nGlory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\nFreedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\nLiberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\nGlory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"收到 以後推呢個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJGphyT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJGphyT.png&h=4ba6e5ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc40dfd6747cf0dc2073c3857c50822a8ac2d1e4","tid":1562923,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:53:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f706afaffe01ba5196390697872003598e03966","tid":1562923,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"一條1000萬view既片既影響力遠遠大於50條多國語言二十萬view既片<br />\n<br />\n希望可以直接加番subtitles就得 唔使再upload多幾條新片 以免分薄d view<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd人見到條片咁多view 就會主動點擊去睇條片 形成雪球效應 越多人睇"},{"pid":"ef04b5c9420fe17636a27707ee5ca9516d10585a","tid":1562923,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f706afaffe01ba5196390697872003598e03966","tid":1562923,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"一條1000萬view既片既影響力遠遠大於50條多國語言二十萬view既片<br />\n<br />\n希望可以直接加番subtitles就得 唔使再upload多幾條新片 以免分薄d view<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd人見到條片咁多view 就會主動點擊去睇條片 形成雪球效應 越多人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2004070754a7834155f7494175044df6e57d1337","tid":1562923,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"大家幫手like埋"},{"pid":"ca5ce3ef5a5cc153d0a543b80d2699ccefd61e7b","tid":1562923,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><